<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(٤٥)</span> بابُ مَا يَجُوزُ مِنْ ذِكْرِ النَّاسِ،<span class="c5"> نَحْوَ قَوْلِهِمُ:</span> الطَّوِيلُ وَالْقَصِيرُ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>-<span class="c5">وَقالَ النَّبِيُّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>:</span> <span class="c2">«مَا يَقُولُ ذُو الْيَدَيْنِ»</span> -<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَمَا لَا يُرَادُ بِهِ شَيْنُ الرَّجُلِ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>